name: Ubik*2
description: I am Ubik. Before the universe was, I am. I made the suns. I made the worlds. I created the lives and the places they inhabit; I move them here, I put them there. They go as I say, they do as I tell them. I am the word and my name is never spoken, the name which no one knows. I am called Ubik, but that is not my name. I am. I shall always be. // A collab between @matheussiq8 and @iglegabriel. // 1024 x 1024 px // Collectors can get in touch for a Prores 422 HQ file.
